high_descs: Walk towards the kitchen door and hang a left at the counter top with the yellow-handled knife.
Walk to the countertop and pick up the yellow-handled knife.
Slice the tomato at the back of the counter and to the right of the plant.
Lay the knife on the handle of the fork that is in the shadow of the plant on the counter.
Pick up the right end slice of the tomato.
Turn and carry the tomato slice to the fridge.

Open the fridge door and place the tomato slice to the left of the head of lettuce on the shelf that is directly above the crisper drawers, close the fridge door and after cooling, open the fridge door, pick up the tomato slice and close the fridge door.
Turn and walk to the recycling bin in the corner of the room to the left of the counter with the sink.
Place the tomato slice in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, refrigerate it, carry it to the recycling bin

high_descs: Walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the yellow knife from the counter.
Cut up the tomato to the right of the plant.
Place the knife on top of the fork on the counter.
Pick up a piece of tomato.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Chill the piece of tomato in the fridge and then pick the piece of tomato up from the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the blue recycling bin in the corner.
Place the piece of tomato in the blue recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled piece of tomato into the recycling bin in the corner.

high_descs: Move to stand at the counter that's to the right of the sink.
Pick up the sharp knife from the counter.
Slice the tomato on the counter next to the plant.
Place the knife on the counter on top of the fork so it forms a cross.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Carry the slice of tomato to the fridge.
Place the tomato in the fridge on the second shelf, close the door, and then remove it after a few seconds.
Carry the slice of tomato to the trash bin in the corner, which is to the left of the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a chilled slice of tomato.
